			(property "Description" "WR-TBL Serie 401B - 5.00 mm Screwless Vertical Entry - 2.0 mm 2 Wires\n\nKIND PROPERTIES\n\nPitch 5 mm\n\nMATERIAL PROPERTIES\n\nInsulator Material PA66\nInsulator Flammability Rating UL94 V-0\nContact Material Brass\nContact Plating Tin\nWire Guard Material Stainless Steel\n\nGENERAL INFORMATION\n\nOperating Temperature -40 up to +105 °C\nCompliance RoHS\n\nELECTRICAL PROPERTIES\n\nIR cULus 10 A\nIR VDE 16 A\nWorking Voltage [cULus] 300 V (AC)\nWorking Voltage [VDE] 450 V (AC)\nWithstanding Voltage [cULus] 2000 V (AC)\nContact Resistance [cULus] 20 mΩ\nContact Resistance [VDE] 20 mΩ\n\nMechanical Properties\n\nWire Strip Length 9 up to 10 (mm)\n\nWire Properties\n\nSolid Wire Section (AWG) 14 to 24 (AWG)\nSolid Wire Section (Metric) 2.08 to 0.205 (mm²)\nStranded Wire Section (AWG) 14 to 24 (AWG)\nStranded Wire Section (Metric) 2.08 to 0.205 (mm²)\n\nCERTIFICATION\n\ncULus Approval E315414\nVDE Approval 40036896\n\nPackaging Properties\n\nPackaging Box\n\nhttps://www.we-online.com/catalog/media/o33321v209%20Family_WR-TBL_6914017000xxB.jpg\n\nDetails see: https://www.we-online.com/catalog/en/TBL_5_00_401B_SCREWLESS_VERTICAL_ENTRY_2_0MM2_WIRES_6914017000XXB/ https://www.we-online.com/catalog/en/TBL_5_00_401B_SCREWLESS_VERTICAL_ENTRY_2_0MM2_WIRES_6914017000XXB/\n\nUpdated by Ella Wu  2019-12-31\n2019(C) Wurth Elektronik"
